ATTRIBUTION / THIRD-PARTY CODE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

AeroShip Saver bundles and adapts the ship save/load engine from the
"Create Aeronautics: Toolgun" mod by enxv233, which is licensed under
CC BY-NC 4.0. All credit for that engine (SubLevelFileStore, the constraint
and contraption restore managers, the blueprint preview, and related code
under the package com.enxv.aeronauticsstructuretool) belongs to enxv233.

Changes made by this project:
  - Removed the @Mod entry class and all item/block/block-entity/creative-tab
    and network-payload registration, replacing them with no-op stubs, so the
    mod registers no synced content.
  - Added a content-free command + keybind front end (com.levi.aeroshipsaver)
    and a redesigned in-game menu.

Because the bundled engine is CC BY-NC 4.0, this project is released under the
same license and is provided strictly for non-commercial use.

This mod also depends on (but does not bundle) Create, Create: Aeronautics,
and Sable, which remain under their own respective licenses.
